NO. 2018-BA-0882 Supreme Court of Louisiana. June 21, 2018

IN RE: COMMITTEE ON BAR ADMISSIONS CFN-17816

Denied. See Supreme Court Rule XVII, § 4(C). Any fees previously paid by applicant to take the February 2018 bar exam may be applied to a subsequent application. See Supreme Court Rule XVII, Appendix A.
